invite_email_template.subject: Your new assessment is ready | ["assessment_title"]
invite_email_template.body:
Hello ["first_name"], 

 

You have been invited for the assessment - ["assessment_title"].

 


The assessment will be accessible for you to attempt between ["exam_start_date"], ["unique_exam_start_time"] to ["exam_end_date"], ["unique_exam_end_time"]. 


We suggest starting the test as soon as possible and ensure that you complete the test within this timeframe.


 

You can start your Main Assessment by clicking here: ["unique_exam_link"]

 

 

To be better prepared, it is recommended to attempt the mock test first, as it helps you to become comfortable with the test interface.

 

 

You can attempt mock test here: ["mock_test_link"]


 

Here are some important Assessment Instructions & FAQ that you need to go through before attempting the assessment.

 

 

For any queries related to the Assessment, please reach out to us on WhatsApp.

 

 

We wish you all the best!

 

Best regards,

Team Topin.

reminder_email_template.subject: Your ["assessment_title"]  Starts in 1 hour
reminder_email_template.body:
Hello ["first_name"], 

 

This is a reminder that ["assessment_title"] will start in one hour. 


Please make sure you have a stable internet connection and a laptop or a desktop with a webcam ready to access the assessment.


You can start your Main Assessment by clicking on this link: ["unique_exam_link"]

 

The assessment will be accessible for you to attempt between ["exam_start_date"], ["unique_exam_start_time"] to ["exam_end_date"], ["unique_exam_end_time"].


We suggest starting the test as soon as possible and ensure that you complete the test within this timeframe.


You are required to be present at your desk at least 10 minutes before the exam start time.

 


To be familiar with the assessment interface, we recommend you take the mock test here: ["mock_test_link"]



Here are some important Exam Instructions & FAQ you need to go through before attempting the exam.


For any queries related to the exam, please reach out to us on WhatsApp

 

 

We wish you all the best for the upcoming exam.

 

Best regards,

Team Topin.
